cs.DL, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the increase in Open Access publication output of German universities, which falls under the category of digital libraries (cs.DL). The analysis of publication output involves data mining and information retrieval techniques (cs.IR). The study also involves the use of cyberinfrastructure and information security (cs.CY) to collect and analyze the data. The topic of Open Access publishing and its impact on citation counts and visibility can also be categorized under computer networks and communications (cs.CR) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
